title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“I remember when I used to see bushels of them,” said Alden “Bud” Miller, gesturing toward a four-door 1923 black-trimmed maroon Buick with a white soft top, wooden hickory smoked wheels and thick white walls. [From the Center Daily Times, State College, Pennsylvania. Submitted by Bill Simon III]
